      <blockquote class="font-display" style="font-style:italic; font-weight:300; font-size:clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.5rem); line-height:1.25; letter-spacing:-0.015em; color:var(--ink); max-width:54rem; margin:0; position:relative; z-index:1;">
        The unEuropean MOOC consortium is no longer a place. It is a contract: open enrolment, named faculty, faithful teaching, proctored assessment, and a credential that someone outside the institution can verify in fifteen seconds.
