        <p style="font-family:'Inter Tight',sans-serif; font-size:15px; color:var(--ink-500); line-height:1.65; margin:0; max-width:34rem; justify-self:end;" class="thesis-rhs">Each school is led by named faculty and authors its own programmes end-to-end. Departments are listed below; click through to see staff, courses, and entry requirements.</p>
